  <brief_title>Study to Compare Clozapine vs Treatment as Usual in People With Intellectual Disability &amp; Treatment-resistant Psychosis</brief_title>
  <acronym>CLOZ-AID</acronym>
  <official_title>A Randomized, Multicenter Clinical Trial to Assess the Efficacy and Safety of Clozapine vs Treatment as Usual for Treatment-resistant Psychosis in Adolescents and Young Adults With Intellectual Disability.</official_title>
