  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This clinical trial will prove whether a large number of people with intellectual disability&#xD;
      and treatment-resistant psychosis could benefit from the use of clozapine. Benefit will mean&#xD;
      a measurable significant improvement in subjects' clinical response and quality of life.&#xD;
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
